Useful resources for implementing auth

Requirements

1. Authenticate user using social networks (twitter, facebook, google)

sample application authenticating with twitter

play documentation: http://www.playframework.org/documentation/latest/ScalaOAuth

app running on: http://poll-opensas.rhcloud.com/
repo: https://github.com/opensas/twitterpoll

authentication: https://github.com/opensas/twitterpoll/blob/master/app/controllers/TwitterAuthenticator.scala

oauth2 sample: https://github.com/jaliss/securesocial/blob/master/module-code/app/securesocial/core/OAuth2Provider.scala

secure social: https://github.com/jaliss/securesocial

2. Secure web service

resources: O'Reilly Restful web service cookbook, chapter 12